<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>A/B Test 실험 페이지</title>
    <style>
        /* 기본 스타일 리셋 */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; }

        /* 비디오 그리드 컨테이너 (3열 구성) */
        .video-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* 개별 비디오 카드 */
        .video-card { width: 100%; cursor: pointer; }

        /* 썸네일 이미지 영역 */
        .thumbnail-container {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            background-color: #efefef;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .thumbnail-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* 비디오 정보 (아이콘 + 텍스트) */
        .video-info { display: flex; gap: 12px; }

        .channel-icon {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #ddd;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .text-content { overflow: hidden; }

        .video-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #0f0f0f;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            /* 두 줄 이상은 말줄임표 처리 */
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .video-meta {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #606060;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="video-grid">
        <div class="video-card">
            <div class="thumbnail-container">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/640x360" alt="Thumbnail A">
            </div>
            <div class="video-info">
                <div class="channel-icon"></div>
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3 class="video-title">실험용 영상 제목 1 - 여기에 제목을 입력하세요</h3>
                    <p class="video-meta">채널명<br>조회수 10만회 • 1일 전</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="video-card">
            <div class="thumbnail-container">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/640x360" alt="Thumbnail B">
            </div>
            <div class="video-info">
                <div class="channel-icon"></div>
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3 class="video-title">실험용 영상 제목 2 - 썸네일 대조군 설정</h3>
                    <p class="video-meta">채널명<br>조회수 5.2만회 • 3시간 전</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="video-card">
            <div class="thumbnail-container">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/640x360" alt="Sponsor">
            </div>
            <div class="video-info">
                <div class="channel-icon"></div>
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3 class="video-title">스폰서 영상 또는 광고 레이아웃 예시</h3>
                    <p class="video-meta"><strong>스폰서</strong> • 업체명</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
